This class provides a skeletal implementation of the Collection interface, to minimize the effort required to implement this interface.

This class implements a vector of bits that grows as needed.

The Calendar class is an abstract class that provides methods for converting between a specific instant in time and a set of calendar fields such asYEAR, MONTH, DAY_OF_MONTH, HOUR, and so on, and for manipulating the calendar fields, such as getting the date of the next week.
Calendar.Builder is used for creating a Calendar from various date-time parameters.
